        <abstract>
            <p>Enjoyed JDH’s visit.</p>
            <p>Mrs Cameron’s photograph of JDH is grand.</p> 
<p>Has heard J. V. Carus will be at Norwich. Suggests JDH mention that <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> was translated by two distinguished naturalists, H. G. Bronn and Carus.</p> 
